<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />For it was not an enemy who rebuked me,</para>

<para style="q1">then I could have borne it;</para>

<para style="q1">neither was it he who hated me who raised himself up against me,</para>

<para style="q1">then I would have hidden myself from him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />But it was you, a man equal to myself,</para>

<para style="q1">my companion and my close friend.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />We had sweet fellowship together;</para>

<para style="q1">we walked in the house of God with the throng.</para>
